`, so it reclones.\r\n\r\n* http://build.osrfoundation.org/job/gazebo-ci-pr_any-homebrew-amd64/717/consoleFull", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Here's an example console message:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>[gazebo] $ hg showconfig paths.default\nERROR: Workspace reports paths.default as http://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo\nwhich looks different than https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo\nso falling back to fresh clone rather than incremental update\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p><code>http</code> doesn't match <code>https</code>, so it reclones.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://build.osrfoundation.org/job/gazebo-ci-pr_any-homebrew-amd64/717/consoleFull\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">http://build.osrfoundation.org/job/gazebo-ci-pr_any-homebrew-amd64/717/consoleFull</a></li>\n</ul>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2016-10-31T21:56:17.434879+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-10-31T22:35:21.599001+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 87}